org.osate.xtext.aadl2.unparsing

Class AadlUnparser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osate.aadl2.modelsupport.modeltraversal.ForAllElement
      • org.osate.aadl2.modelsupport.modeltraversal.AadlProcessingSwitch
        • org.osate.xtext.aadl2.unparsing.AadlUnparser

  • public class AadlUnparser
extends AadlProcessingSwitch
    This class implements the converter from an AADL object model to textual AADL. The generated text is made available as a string buffer.
    Author:
    phf
